result.description:
This report will have a two-fold approach to the collection and analysis of the status of standards development for mass-market drones:
- on one side, it will consider any progress and/or deviation in the standards already collected and analysed in D3.1. They will be integrated and complemented with the new regulations and standards emerged in the meantime at a global level;
- in addition, particular focus will be put on the emerging standards needed for the safe and reliable development of U-Space.
